bioghist.p:
Names include: 
William Appleton (founding member); 
Henry Codman; 
Peter Coffin and members of the Coffin family; 
John Hancock (possibly the son of the American Founding Father of the same name); 
Harrison Gray Otis; 
William Shimmin (founding member); 
George Sullivan; 
Daniel Webster (American orator and politician, 1782-1852); 
Francis Wilby
